{"tid":1382550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港抗議中的「陣地社工」：走在最前線的「情緒消防員」 － BBC News 中文","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:09:43.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83b8a4c83b7613e14b25410e83e47bd1ff55ba17","tid":1382550,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o1VBF_1TGco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo1VBF_1TGco&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ec09c144\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o1VBF_1TGco</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港，當防暴警察配備全副武裝與催淚瓦斯，示威者戴上頭盔、口罩並拿著雨傘與之對峙之時，有這樣一群人幾乎毫無裝備，光憑一台擴音機，在這兩群人的中央嘗試喊話，化解衝突。<br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修正案抗議引發6月12日大規模警民衝突之後，一支名為「陣地社工」的義務團隊正式成立。BBC中文記者走訪這一支嘗試在示威者與防暴警察之間調停的社工團隊。<br />\n<br />\n採訪/製作：斯影，葉靖斯"},{"pid":"c0ea703ae34008dff2fcbb94d098e614f0dbf750","tid":1382550,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"認真咁講，有邊件黑警俾陳虹秀target感化<br />\n唔崩潰都幾晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都好多謝佢地助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd6873039bf6da49bc2f88b67bd7aa5447ba35f","tid":1382550,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0ea703ae34008dff2fcbb94d098e614f0dbf750","tid":1382550,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"認真咁講，有邊件黑警俾陳虹秀target感化<br />\n唔崩潰都幾晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都好多謝佢地助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"鳳凰幻魔拳<img src